{"tid":1693684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咁嘅黃店重值唔值得懲罰？","createTime":"2019-11-04T17:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T10:02:08.000Z","uid":120945,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4df73b49058070dd39e889b8470f4b5292f8a9a4","tid":1693684,"uid":120945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:48:03.000Z","msg":"近排元朗開咗間豆漿店 開頭都覺得幾新奇，主打濃豆漿，sell真材實料<br />\n但係個branding同設計就有啲熟口熟面？<br />\n<br />\n話說台灣有間早餐店専賣豆乳製品叫二吉軒，主打文青風<br />\n重請左日本插畫家Noritake同佢哋畫咗插畫做招牌<br />\n係台灣都小有名氣，之後台灣就多咗文青風豆漿店<br />\n<br />\n但係咪覺得個插畫好熟口面？<br />\n係呀，你冇睇錯呀，係喜茶logo，到後期乜乜酸奶君都抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上：二吉軒<br />\n下：元朗新店logo又係眼耳口鼻線條樣嘅？ <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Uw8ro0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Uw8ro0.jpg&h=a07cdb5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上：二吉軒雪櫃<br />\n下： beanlab 雪櫃<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6cLtCq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6cLtCq.jpg&h=80a60c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上：二吉軒店面<br />\n下： beanlab 店面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a0Vtrpa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa0Vtrpa.jpg&h=c0f6df60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上：二吉軒膠樽<br />\n下： beanlab 膠樽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5i3fhy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5i3fhy.jpg&h=e4cd87cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n間野賣哂廣吿，話自己去台灣飲豆漿做參考<br />\n乜參考到連branding都咁似？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p3v1Mpi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp3v1Mpi.png&h=0e2fcaff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋有係店面痴文宣，同會係ig post啲圖表示自己係黃店，暗示叫人懲罰佢<br />\n本身罷食藍店支持小店係件好事，但點解要懲罰一間咁可疑又抄襲人嘅店？<br />\n一間咁嘅店，同Miniso,喜茶,小米有咩分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人唔好學埋大陸啲野啦"},{"pid":"898f520364c0675b3683af1b9c5a0e9108fb55a5","tid":1693684,"uid":176081,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"其實就算係黃店 我都會考慮味道同價錢 同埋理念 好多野 唔會單單因為佢係黃店就盲目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeabe49096351d0e0a7ce8fa7a7b6f198c72492c","tid":1693684,"uid":58038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"898f520364c0675b3683af1b9c5a0e9108fb55a5","tid":1693684,"uid":176081,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"其實就算係黃店 我都會考慮味道同價錢 同埋理念 好多野 唔會單單因為佢係黃店就盲目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:54:33.000Z","msg":"難食 貴都唔割<br />\n藍轉黃扮綠 退100步黎講都仲可以接受<br />\n但連基本道德都無算乜撚野同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d62a19aa859e97f3544abaef28f7fc98e84a56","tid":1693684,"uid":120906,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:56:41.000Z","msg":"佢抄人同政治立場冇關係，好飲咪飲，最緊要真係黃"},{"pid":"dcc9ede519d91b2d28d5f198d5eba6275130d0c1","tid":1693684,"uid":49847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:00:57.000Z","msg":"間間都咁上下架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d663f015c91ac1d437e2b73eb0050b2989edb7","tid":1693684,"uid":49847,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"dcc9ede519d91b2d28d5f198d5eba6275130d0c1","tid":1693684,"uid":49847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:00:57.000Z","msg":"間間都咁上下架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:02:31.000Z","msg":"同埋一D都唔似 唔知你咩居心"},{"pid":"275e3a88108d82f7b487ab13e33aa8261cfdca69","tid":1693684,"uid":263806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:03:05.000Z","msg":"個樽真係最好改下..其他我都覺得唔算太過份<br />\n<br />\n屌你我是酸奶君同喜茶個logo真係講起就嬲<img src=\"/assets/f